Document: RDVertexAttribute
Path: godot/classes/class_rdvertexattribute.rst
Summary: Properties and their default values for the RDVertexAttribute class.

- binding (int): Attribute binding index. Default: 4294967295
- format (DataFormat): Vertex data format (from RenderingDevice_DataFormat enum). Default: 232
- frequency (VertexFrequency): Update frequency (from RenderingDevice_VertexFrequency enum). Default: 0
- location (int): Shader attribute location. Default: 0
- offset (int): Byte offset within the vertex buffer. Default: 0
- stride (int): Byte distance between consecutive vertex entries. Default: 0
